# Building Categories & Costs Reference:
####################

# RESOURCE BUILDINGS:
# - Lumberyard: 50 wood, 0 iron, 10 gold (5 min build) - Produces wood
# - Mine: 30 wood, 10 iron, 25 gold (7.5 min build) - Produces iron, gold, silver
# - Plantation: 40 wood, 0 iron, 15 gold (6 min build) - Produces sugar, tobacco, cotton, coffee
# - Farm: 25 wood, 0 iron, 5 gold (4 min build) - Produces grain, rum

# TRADE BUILDINGS:
# - Trade Center: 100 wood, 50 iron, 100 gold (10 min build) - Enables trading

# MILITARY BUILDINGS:
# - Shipyard: 150 wood, 100 iron, 200 gold (15 min build) - Ship construction/repairs
# - Fort: 100 wood, 200 iron, 150 gold (20 min build) - Island defense

# INFRASTRUCTURE BUILDINGS:
# - Warehouse: 80 wood, 20 iron, 30 gold (5 min build) - Storage capacity
# - Dock: 60 wood, 30 iron, 20 gold (6 min build) - Ship docking/trade
# - Tavern: 40 wood, 10 iron, 50 gold (5 min build) - Crew recruitment/morale